{"tid":1566880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DLLM 呢間餐廳老闆𨳒我哋香港人係廢柴係暴徒！","createTime":"2019-09-13T19:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T01:58:56.000Z","uid":59985,"like":133,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"6f0e63e59c8b73746c3a2711fecc167c3a70cfca","tid":1566880,"uid":59985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T19:46:16.000Z","msg":"代朋友出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朋友之前做過呢間叫胡爐/醉胡爐（尖沙咀/老銅）既餐廳，所以有留意開佢其中一個老闆個Facebook！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個老闆自稱係深紅係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後成撚日𨳒鳩抗爭者係口罩黨，仲有818果170萬香港人係廢柴同盟</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">之前仲見佢話我哋個撚個都係暴徒</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身琴日朋友都係facebook group出咗post叫人罷吃，但個仆街port鳩我朋友facebook，仲將地球post轉返曬做私人post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然佢𨳒鳩我哋，做嘜仲要俾錢佢賺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面係朋友之前cap低既圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zfcLXJT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzfcLXJT.jpg&h=707d5f4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a821de2e7d044c8ff1058adec4c5731d4cb1abf6","tid":1566880,"uid":59985,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T19:47:16.000Z","msg":"自推十下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p